@startuml 时序图_报名缴费
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title 用户报名缴费时序图

actor "家长/学员" as User
participant "浏览器" as Browser
participant "Flask路由\n/login /courses" as Flask
participant "报名缴费逻辑\n/enroll /payment" as EnrollLogic
participant "安全工具\ncaptcha verify" as Security
database "SQLite\ncalligraphy_system.db" as DB

== 登录与浏览 ==
User -> Browser: 打开登录页
Browser -> Flask: GET /login
Flask -> Security: check_captcha(input)
Security --> Flask: bool
Flask -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
DB --> Flask: user record
Flask -> Security: verify_password(password, hash)
Security --> Flask: bool
Flask --> Browser: 渲染首页，设置Session

User -> Browser: 点击课程列表
Browser -> Flask: GET /courses
Flask -> DB: SELECT * FROM courses
DB --> Flask: courses[]
Flask --> Browser: 渲染 courses.html

User -> Browser: 选择课程，查看详情
Browser -> Flask: GET /course/<id>
Flask -> DB: SELECT * FROM courses WHERE id=?
DB --> Flask: course record
Flask --> Browser: 渲染 course_detail.html

== 报名流程 ==
User -> Browser: 点击"立即报名"
Browser -> EnrollLogic: POST /enroll/1
EnrollLogic -> Flask: 检查Session[user_id]
Flask --> EnrollLogic: user_id
EnrollLogic -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id=?
DB --> EnrollLogic: user info
EnrollLogic -> EnrollLogic: 检查信息完整性
EnrollLogic -> DB: SELECT * FROM courses WHERE id=?
DB --> EnrollLogic: course info
EnrollLogic -> EnrollLogic: 检查余量、重复报名
EnrollLogic --> Browser: JSON {success: true}

== 缴费流程 ==
User -> Browser: 确认缴费
Browser -> EnrollLogic: POST /payment
EnrollLogic -> EnrollLogic: 从Session获取course_id
EnrollLogic -> DB: SELECT * FROM courses WHERE id=? AND current<max
DB --> EnrollLogic: course record
EnrollLogic -> DB: SELECT * FROM enrollments WHERE user_id=? AND course_id=?
DB --> EnrollLogic: null

EnrollLogic -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
EnrollLogic -> DB: INSERT enrollments (paid)
DB --> EnrollLogic: enrollment_id
EnrollLogic -> DB: INSERT alternate_courses
EnrollLogic -> DB: UPDATE courses SET current_students = current_students + 1
EnrollLogic -> DB: COMMIT

alt 事务成功
    EnrollLogic --> Browser: JSON {success: true, message: "缴费成功"}
    Browser --> User: 显示报名成功
else 事务失败
    EnrollLogic -> DB: ROLLBACK
    EnrollLogic --> Browser: JSON {success: false, message: "缴费失败"}
    Browser --> User: 显示错误提示
end

@enduml